title: file path list
sql_command: select title as value_, id as key_ from file_paths.csv;

title: file path
sql_command: select path,file from file_paths.csv where id = 1;

title: data select
sql_command: select top 200 [f2] as item_id,f3 as [カラム論理名],[f11] as [カラム物理名],f19 as [データ型],f23 as [桁数],f25 as [制度],[f27] as [NULL],f29 as [一意],[f31] as [主キー],f33 as [デフォルト],f36 as [説明] from [%1$] where isnumeric([f2]) and [f11] is not null;
